channel.title: [HELP!] Any RS2 Server that has Jad?
channel.description:
I've been getting killed by Jad all the time. Does any RS2 Private Server have Jad so I can practice on him?
Please help, I really need to practice killing Jad, hes level 702 and keeps killing me. I am working 3 hours to get to him and dying :( It also costs about 300k each round and I've lost 16 million already.
Thanks.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: April 14, 2008, 09:36:48 PM[/size][hr]If any mod of an RS2 server can make me a strong account just temporarily so I can practice I'd really appreciate it cuz I dont think I will be able to start an entirely new game just to practice on Jad.
Thanks.
